564
00:29:31,290 --> 00:29:32,090
Godmother.

565
00:29:32,330 --> 00:29:34,460
Mom, why did you say things like that?

566
00:29:34,460 --> 00:29:36,890
However, let me be clear upfront.

567
00:29:37,970 --> 00:29:39,290
No matter what kind of ceremony

568
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:40,550
you two have in the future,

569
00:29:41,100 --> 00:29:42,880
don't ask me to take charge of it.

570
00:29:43,730 --> 00:29:45,640
I'm already too busy with my own affairs.

571
00:29:46,170 --> 00:29:47,410
As for your own affairs,

572
00:29:47,410 --> 00:29:49,210
you'll have to figure them out yourselves.

573
00:29:49,450 --> 00:29:52,010
Once everything is ready, just let me know.

574
00:29:55,010 --> 00:29:55,810
Su,

575
00:29:56,410 --> 00:29:57,170
you've always

576
00:29:57,490 --> 00:30:00,650
been so good to me and Nian.

577
00:30:01,170 --> 00:30:02,180
I really appreciate it.

578
00:30:04,750 --> 00:30:05,950
As for Nian's matters,

579
00:30:06,710 --> 00:30:08,420
I won't trouble you with them anymore.

580
00:30:08,820 --> 00:30:10,460
Let her decide for herself.

581
00:30:11,070 --> 00:30:11,870
Mom,

582
00:30:12,610 --> 00:30:13,640
are you saying this

583
00:30:14,210 --> 00:30:16,600
because you still haven't truly accepted us being together?

584
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,360
Nian,

585
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:21,240
I've already made the biggest concession I can.

586
00:30:21,810 --> 00:30:24,370
You can't ask me to try harder, can you?

587
00:30:25,570 --> 00:30:26,360
Got it.

588
00:30:27,170 --> 00:30:29,250
Alright, I've said everything

589
00:30:29,250 --> 00:30:30,250
I needed to say.

590
00:30:30,800 --> 00:30:32,160
You should be going now, shouldn't you?

591
00:30:32,450 --> 00:30:34,450
Don't let this interfere with your work.

592
00:30:34,650 --> 00:30:35,680
Mom, I'm not leaving.

593
00:30:35,930 --> 00:30:36,850
I want to stay here with you.

594
00:30:36,930 --> 00:30:37,740
Director Su,

595
00:30:38,190 --> 00:30:39,210
I'd like to take a few days off.

596
00:30:39,730 --> 00:30:40,310
Okay.

597
00:30:40,650 --> 00:30:41,650
What are you talking about?

598
00:30:41,650 --> 00:30:43,490
Aren't you afraid of getting fired?

599
00:30:43,660 --> 00:30:45,420
Hurry up and leave. Otherwise, I'll chase you out.

600
00:30:45,420 --> 00:30:46,130
I'm not leaving, Mom.

601
00:30:46,130 --> 00:30:47,410
I'll see you two off to the door.

602
00:30:47,410 --> 00:30:47,650
No, no, no.

603
00:30:47,650 --> 00:30:48,010
Godmother.

604
00:30:48,010 --> 00:30:48,970
Be careful, Mom.

605
00:30:49,490 --> 00:30:50,210
I'm fine.

606
00:30:50,210 --> 00:30:51,170
Be careful.

607
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:52,050
I'm fine.

608
00:30:52,050 --> 00:30:53,020
I'll let you see.

609
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:09,820
Get in the car.

610
00:31:09,850 --> 00:31:10,600
I'll take care of Aunt Dai.

611
00:31:10,650 --> 00:31:11,450
Just go.

612
00:31:11,830 --> 00:31:13,100
Mom, I'm leaving then.

613
00:31:13,300 --> 00:31:13,780
Just go.

614
00:31:14,870 --> 00:31:15,580
I'm really leaving.

615
00:31:16,050 --> 00:31:16,650
Go.

616
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:17,310
Just go.

617
00:31:17,520 --> 00:31:18,330
Go now.

618
00:31:18,610 --> 00:31:19,650
Godmother, I'm leaving.

619
00:31:19,720 --> 00:31:20,570
Mom, I'm really leaving.

620
00:31:20,600 --> 00:31:21,410
Get in the car.

621
00:31:21,740 --> 00:31:22,500
Go.

622
00:31:30,250 --> 00:31:31,690
Mom, remember to call me.

623
00:31:33,760 --> 00:31:34,510
Su.

624
00:31:41,610 --> 00:31:43,030
Aunt Dai, let's go back.

625
00:31:49,160 --> 00:31:49,950
Su,

626
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,720
give the household registration book to Nian.

627
00:31:53,770 --> 00:31:55,650
Thank you for everything you've done for us.

628
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:24,510
Here.

629
00:32:27,180 --> 00:32:28,560
Mom asked me to give it to you.

630
00:32:31,690 --> 00:32:33,010
I'm following Mom's instructions.

631
00:32:35,470 --> 00:32:37,300
This is the biggest concession I can make.

632
00:32:49,580 --> 00:32:50,370
Gu Nian,

633
00:32:51,780 --> 00:32:53,860
from now on, we won't interfere with you and Feng Huanan anymore.

634
00:32:54,570 --> 00:32:56,490
But there are some things you must keep in mind.

635
00:32:57,210 --> 00:32:58,020
What things?

636
00:32:58,470 --> 00:32:59,850
The Revisit Project.

637
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:02,210
We made a mistake, so we should fix it as soon as possible.

638
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:03,740
What should we do?

639
00:33:04,090 --> 00:33:06,210
I heard that Mr. Li is very angry.

640
00:33:07,820 --> 00:33:08,490
Being upfront and honest

641
00:33:08,490 --> 00:33:10,170
is the best way to show sincerity.

642
00:33:10,760 --> 00:33:12,080
Mr. Li is someone who values relationships.

643
00:33:13,650 --> 00:33:14,610
He will understand.

644
00:33:16,170 --> 00:33:17,120
But I'm warning you,

645
00:33:17,690 --> 00:33:18,960
before you see Feng Huanan,

646
00:33:18,980 --> 00:33:20,330
