659
00:35:05,970 --> 00:35:06,250
How is it?

660
00:35:06,250 --> 00:35:07,690
You haven't even gotten in.

661
00:35:07,690 --> 00:35:08,610
I feel like my chest

662
00:35:08,610 --> 00:35:09,050
