663
00:35:12,070 --> 00:35:13,760
That's right.

664
00:35:13,850 --> 00:35:15,050
I... I can't move now.

665
00:35:15,050 --> 00:35:16,220
I can't move at all.

666
00:35:16,220 --> 00:35:17,570
You're just too cute.

667
00:35:18,900 --> 00:35:19,450
Nian.

668
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:21,960
Why did you call me over

669
00:35:22,770 --> 00:35:23,610
so urgently?

670
00:35:23,610 --> 00:35:24,970
I'm still running orders.

671
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:27,010
I placed your next order.

672
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:28,040
Stop kidding.

673
00:35:28,340 --> 00:35:30,340
You don't even have a car. Why did you place an order?

674
00:35:30,810 --> 00:35:31,690
It's our order.

675
00:35:32,950 --> 00:35:33,750
Huanan,

676
00:35:34,170 --> 00:35:35,370
