677
00:35:36,650 --> 00:35:38,170
Let's get married!

678
00:35:38,730 --> 00:35:39,530
Really?

679
00:35:40,980 --> 00:35:41,770
Really?

680
00:35:42,330 --> 00:35:42,970
I...

681
00:35:46,490 --> 00:35:47,330
Is it true, Nian?

682
00:35:47,330 --> 00:35:48,050
It's true.

683
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:02,000
You must reschedule the wedding date.

684
